WEBVTT

00:10.080 --> 00:14.220
CHAPTER XIII. GETTING INTO THE RIGHT BUSINESS

00:14.570 --> 00:19.840
Success in any particular business depends for one thing upon your possessing in a well-developed

00:19.840 --> 00:25.920
state the faculties required in that business. Without good musical faculty no one can succeed

00:25.920 --> 00:31.220
as a teacher of music. Without well-developed mechanical faculties no one can achieve great

00:31.220 --> 00:36.580
success in any of the mechanical trades. Without tech and the commercial faculties no one

00:36.580 --> 00:42.000
can succeed in mercantile pursuits. But to possess in a well-developed state the faculties

00:42.000 --> 00:47.020
required in your particular vocation does not ensure getting rich. There are musicians

00:47.020 --> 00:52.780
who have remarkable talent and who yet remain poor. There are blacksmiths, carpenters and

00:52.780 --> 00:58.200
so on who have excellent mechanical ability but who do not get rich. And there are merchants

00:58.200 --> 01:03.700
with good faculties for dealing with men who nevertheless fail. The different faculties

01:03.700 --> 01:09.180
are tools. It is essential to have good tools but it is also essential that the tools should

01:09.180 --> 01:15.580
be used in the right way. One man can take a sharp saw, a square, a good plane and so

01:15.580 --> 01:21.000
on and build a handsome article of furniture. Another man can take the same tools and set

01:21.000 --> 01:27.420
to work to duplicate the article but his production will be a botch. He does not know how to use

01:27.420 --> 01:33.040
good tools in a successful way. The various faculties of your mind are the tools with

01:33.040 --> 01:37.900
which you must do the work which is to make you rich. It will be easier for you to succeed

01:37.900 --> 01:42.920
if you get into a business for which you are well equipped with mental tools. Generally

01:42.920 --> 01:48.280
speaking you will do best in that business which will use your strongest faculties, the

01:48.280 --> 01:52.880
one for which you are naturally best fitted. But there are limitations to this statement

01:52.880 --> 01:58.420
also. No man should regard his vocation as being irrevocably fixed by the tendencies

01:58.420 --> 02:03.440
with which he was born. You can get rich in any business for if you have not the right

02:03.440 --> 02:08.760
talent you can develop that talent. It merely means that you will have to make your tools

02:08.760 --> 02:13.880
as you go along instead of confining yourself to the use of those with which you were born.

02:13.880 --> 02:18.880
It will be easier for you to succeed in a vocation for which you already have the talents

02:18.880 --> 02:24.920
in a well developed state. But you can succeed in any vocation for you can develop any rudimentary

02:24.920 --> 02:30.260
talent and there is no talent of which you have not at least the rudiment. You will get

02:30.260 --> 02:35.160
rich most easily in point of effort if you do that for which you are best fitted but

02:35.160 --> 02:40.920
you will get rich most satisfactorily if you do that which you want to do. Doing what you

02:40.920 --> 02:46.380
want to do is life and there is no real satisfaction in living if we are compelled to be forever

02:46.380 --> 02:51.600
doing something which we do not like to do and can never do what we want to do. And it

02:51.600 --> 02:56.440
is certain that you can do what you want to do. The desire to do it is proof that you

02:56.440 --> 03:02.400
have within you the power which can do it. Desire is a manifestation of power. The desire

03:02.400 --> 03:06.620
to play music is the power which can play music seeking expression and development.

03:07.020 --> 03:11.980
The desire to invent mechanical devices is the mechanical talent seeking expression and

03:11.980 --> 03:17.180
development. Where there is no power either developed or undeveloped to do a thing there

03:17.180 --> 03:22.020
is never any desire to do that thing. And where there is strong desire to do a thing

03:22.020 --> 03:27.180
it is certain proof that the power to do it is strong and only requires to be developed

03:27.180 --> 03:33.340
and applied in the right way. All things else being equal it is best to select a business

03:33.340 --> 03:37.800
for which you have the best developed talent but if you have a strong desire to engage

03:37.800 --> 03:42.660
in any particular line of work you should select that work as the ultimate end at which

03:42.660 --> 03:47.980
you aim. You can do what you want to do and it is your right and privilege to follow the

03:47.980 --> 03:54.160
business or avocation which will be most congenial and pleasant. You are not obliged to do what

03:54.160 --> 03:58.960
you do not like to do and you should not do it except as the means to bring you to the

03:58.960 --> 04:04.780
of the thing you want to do. If there are past mistakes whose consequences have placed you in

04:04.780 --> 04:09.900
an undesirable business or environment you may be obliged for some time to do what you do not like

04:09.900 --> 04:15.100
to do but you can make the doing of it pleasant by knowing that it is making it possible for you

04:15.100 --> 04:20.220
to come to the doing of what you want to do. If you feel that you are not in the right vocation

04:20.220 --> 04:25.360
do not act too hastily in trying to get into another one. The best way generally to change

04:25.360 --> 04:30.540
business or environment is by growth. Do not be afraid to make a sudden and radical change

04:30.540 --> 04:35.800
if the opportunity is presented and you feel after careful consideration that it is the right

04:35.800 --> 04:41.520
opportunity but never take sudden or radical action when you are in doubt as to the wisdom

04:41.520 --> 04:47.440
of doing so. There is never any hurry on the creative plane and there is no lack of opportunity.

04:48.200 --> 04:53.400
When you get out of the competitive mind you will understand that you never need to act hastily.

04:53.400 --> 04:59.100
No one else is going to beat you to the thing you want to do. There is enough for all. If one

04:59.100 --> 05:04.200
space is taken another and a better one will be opened for you a little further on. There is

05:04.200 --> 05:10.040
plenty of time. When you are in doubt, wait. Fall back on the contemplation of your vision

05:10.040 --> 05:15.480
and increase your faith and purpose and by all means in times of doubt and indecision

05:15.480 --> 05:20.960
cultivate gratitude. A day or two spent in contemplating the vision of what you want

05:20.960 --> 05:26.840
and in earnest thanksgiving that you are getting it will bring your mind into such close relationship

05:26.840 --> 05:32.660
with the Supreme that you will make no mistake when you do act. There is a mind which knows all

05:32.660 --> 05:37.620
there is to know and you can come into close unity with this mind by faith and the purpose

05:37.620 --> 05:44.080
to advance in life if you have deep gratitude. Mistakes come from acting hastily or from acting

05:44.080 --> 05:50.220
in fear or doubt or in forgetfulness of the right motive which is more life to all and less to none.

05:50.780 --> 05:55.540
As you go on in the certain way opportunities will come to you in increasing number

05:55.540 --> 06:00.880
and you will need to be very steady in your faith and purpose and to keep in close touch with the

06:00.880 --> 06:07.080
old mind by reverent gratitude. Do all that you can do in a perfect manner every day but do it

06:07.080 --> 06:13.860
without haste, worry or fear. Go as fast as you can but never hurry. Remember that in the moment

06:13.860 --> 06:19.620
you begin to hurry you cease to be a creator and become a competitor you drop back upon the old

06:19.620 --> 06:26.060
plane again. Whenever you find yourself hurrying call a halt. Fix your attention on the mental

06:26.060 --> 06:31.360
image of the thing you want and begin to give thanks that you are getting it. The exercise

06:31.360 --> 06:38.880
of gratitude will never fail to strengthen your faith and renew your purpose. End of chapter 13

